 Brandon Herrera, extending House incumbents=E2=80=99 nearly unbroken strea=
k of primary wins. But Gonzales=E2=80=99s razor-thin margin of victory=E2=
=80=94a mere 407 votes out of 29,639=E2=80=94suggests that institutionalist=
 House Republicans like Tom Cole of Oklahoma and Mike Simpson of Idaho have=
