* Cuellar vs. Furman: Speaking of pickup opportunities, we now know who Dem=
ocrat Henry Cuellar=E2=80=99s Republican challenger will be in Texas=E2=80=
=99s 28th district: Jay Furman. Cuellar, of course, is currently under indi=
