ll be our turn. We=E2=80=99ll go state by state and do what we did before <=
i>Dobbs</i>.<br/><br/><b>That sugar high will drive Democrats and pro-choic=
e Republicans out to vote in this election cycle, though. What are G.O.P. c=
andidates saying to you about how they plan to navigate this environment?</=
